{"tha-ap44:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap44:0.2":"Upalivagga ","tha-ap44:0.3":"2 Sonakolivisattheraapadana ","tha-ap44:1.1":"“Anomadassissa munino, ","tha-ap44:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap44:1.3":"Sudhaya lepanam katva, ","tha-ap44:1.4":"cankamam karayim aham. ","tha-ap44:2.1":"Nanavannehi pupphehi, ","tha-ap44:2.2":"cankamam santharim aham; ","tha-ap44:2.3":"Akase vitanam katva, ","tha-ap44:2.4":"bhojayim buddhamuttamam. ","tha-ap44:3.1":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap44:3.2":"abhivadetvana subbatam; ","tha-ap44:3.3":"Dighasalam bhagavato, ","tha-ap44:3.4":"niyyadesimaham tada. ","tha-ap44:4.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap44:4.2":"sattha loke anuttaro; ","tha-ap44:4.3":"Patiggahesi bhagava, ","tha-ap44:4.4":"anukampaya cakkhuma. ","tha-ap44:5.1":"Patiggahetvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap44:5.2":"dakkhineyyo sadevake; ","tha-ap44:5.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap44:5.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap44:6.1":"‘Yo so hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap44:6.2":"dighasalam adasi me; ","tha-ap44:6.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap44:6.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap44:7.1":"Imassa maccukalamhi, ","tha-ap44:7.2":"punnakammasamangino; ","tha-ap44:7.3":"Sahassayuttassaratho, ","tha-ap44:7.4":"upatthissati tavade. ","tha-ap44:8.1":"Tena yanenayam poso, ","tha-ap44:8.2":"devalokam gamissati; ","tha-ap44:8.3":"Anumodissare deva, ","tha-ap44:8.4":"sampatte kusalabbhave. ","tha-ap44:9.1":"Maharaham byamham settham, ","tha-ap44:9.2":"ratanamattikalepanam; ","tha-ap44:9.3":"Kutagaravarupetam, ","tha-ap44:9.4":"byamham ajjhavasissati. ","tha-ap44:10.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap44:10.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap44:10.3":"Pancavisati kappani, ","tha-ap44:10.4":"devaraja bhavissati. ","tha-ap44:11.1":"Sattasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap44:11.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap44:11.3":"Yasodharasanama te, ","tha-ap44:11.4":"sabbepi ekanamaka. ","tha-ap44:12.1":"Dve sampatti anubhotva, ","tha-ap44:12.2":"Vaddhetva punnasancayam; ","tha-ap44:12.3":"Atthavisatikappamhi, ","tha-ap44:12.4":"Cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap44:13.1":"Tatrapi byamham pavaram, ","tha-ap44:13.2":"vissakammena mapitam; ","tha-ap44:13.3":"Dasasaddavivittam tam, ","tha-ap44:13.4":"puramajjhavasissati. ","tha-ap44:14.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap44:14.2":"bhumipalo mahiddhiko; ","tha-ap44:14.3":"Okkako nama namena, ","tha-ap44:14.4":"raja ratthe bhavissati. ","tha-ap44:15.1":"Solasitthisahassanam, ","tha-ap44:15.2":"sabbasam pavara ca sa; ","tha-ap44:15.3":"Abhijata khattiyani, ","tha-ap44:15.4":"nava putte janessati. ","tha-ap44:16.1":"Nava putte janetvana, ","tha-ap44:16.2":"khattiyani marissati; ","tha-ap44:16.3":"Taruni ca piya kanna, ","tha-ap44:16.4":"mahesittam karissati. ","tha-ap44:17.1":"Okkakam tosayitvana, ","tha-ap44:17.2":"varam kanna labhissati; ","tha-ap44:17.3":"Varam laddhana sa kanna, ","tha-ap44:17.4":"putte pabbajayissati. ","tha-ap44:18.1":"Pabbajita ca te sabbe, ","tha-ap44:18.2":"gamissanti naguttamam; ","tha-ap44:18.3":"Jatibhedabhaya sabbe, ","tha-ap44:18.4":"bhaginihi vasissare. ","tha-ap44:19.1":"Eka ca kanna byadhihi, ","tha-ap44:19.2":"bhavissati parikkhata; ","tha-ap44:19.3":"Ma no jati pabhijjiti, ","tha-ap44:19.4":"nikhanissanti khattiya. ","tha-ap44:20.1":"Khattiyo niharitvana, ","tha-ap44:20.2":"taya saddhim vasissati; ","tha-ap44:20.3":"Bhavissati tada bhedo, ","tha-ap44:20.4":"okkakakulasambhavo. ","tha-ap44:21.1":"Tesam paja bhavissanti, ","tha-ap44:21.2":"koliya nama jatiya; ","tha-ap44:21.3":"Tattha manusakam bhogam, ","tha-ap44:21.4":"anubhossatinappakam. ","tha-ap44:22.1":"Tamha kaya cavitvana, ","tha-ap44:22.2":"devalokam gamissati; ","tha-ap44:22.3":"Tatrapi pavaram byamham, ","tha-ap44:22.4":"labhissati manoramam. ","tha-ap44:23.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap44:23.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap44:23.3":"Agantvana manussattam, ","tha-ap44:23.4":"sono nama bhavissati. ","tha-ap44:24.1":"Araddhaviriyo pahitatto, ","tha-ap44:24.2":"Padaham satthu sasane; ","tha-ap44:24.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap44:24.4":"Nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap44:25.1":"Anantadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap44:25.2":"gotamo sakyapungavo; ","tha-ap44:25.3":"Visesannu mahaviro, ","tha-ap44:25.4":"aggatthane thapessati’. ","tha-ap44:26.1":"Vutthamhi deve caturangulamhi, ","tha-ap44:26.2":"Tine anileritaanganamhi; ","tha-ap44:26.3":"Thatvana yogassa payuttatadino, ","tha-ap44:26.4":"Tatottarim paramata na vijjati. ","tha-ap44:27.1":"Uttame damathe danto, ","tha-ap44:27.2":"cittam me supanihitam; ","tha-ap44:27.3":"Bharo me ohito sabbo, ","tha-ap44:27.4":"nibbutomhi anasavo. ","tha-ap44:28.1":"Angiraso mahanago, ","tha-ap44:28.2":"abhijatova kesari; ","tha-ap44:28.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap44:28.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap44:29.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap44:29.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap44:29.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap44:30.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sono koliviso thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap44:31.1":"Sonakolivisattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}